        {
            "title": "馬鞍山錦豐苑J座低層2房戶 自由市場價$460萬成交 (另有本日最新成交)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZzfPw_N4hzD5NyCCuSJ.uw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/f9c70364dded845caf00afd01299a044\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E9%8C%A6%E8%B1%90%E8%8B%91j%E5%BA%A7%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A42%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%83%B9-460%E8%90%AC%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4-%E5%8F%A6%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4-080306744.html",
